        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down, Beckenham</placeName>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>My father begs me to thank you for communicating to him the curious case of the insects.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> The fact is an interesting one, but as he is at work on different subjects he will not take advantage of yr kind offer of sending 〈speci〉mens</p>
<p>Yrs truly | Francis Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

